Dialogue: 0,00:10:21.08,00:10:24.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なぜ　お前が俺のチャクラを持ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have my chakra?!
Dialogue: 0,00:10:24.70,00:10:28.90,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前が死んだとき　完全に俺は\Nお前から抜けたはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When you died,\NI extracted myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:28.90,00:10:31.58,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,久しぶりだな　八尾。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Eight Tails.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:31.58,00:10:34.41,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まさか　こんな再会をするとはな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To think we'd see each other\Nunder these circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:34.41,00:10:39.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺も残念だ。　少しは\Nお前を見込んでたんだがな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I had high hopes for you...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:39.73,00:10:42.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺たちは\Nまんまと　はめられたのさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We were completely fooled.
Dialogue: 0,00:10:42.20,00:10:45.20,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,誰に？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,00:10:45.20,00:10:48.69,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,３０年前…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,00:10:55.08,00:10:57.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((エーか。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Ay.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:00.05,00:11:03.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,迂闊に俺に近づかないでくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch how you approach me.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:03.05,00:11:05.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,どうした　眠れないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:05.70,00:11:10.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ああ　満月の夜は特にな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,especially during a full moon.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:10.31,00:11:15.76,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まるで　俺の心に\Nぽっかりと開いた穴だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the big hole in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:15.76,00:11:18.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まだ　それを\N埋める何かは見つからないのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You still haven't found\Nsomething to fill it?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:18.98,00:11:21.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,見つからないだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably won't.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:21.50,00:11:27.70,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,体は　ここにあっても\N俺の心は何も生きちゃいない。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm physically here...\Nmy heart is dead.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:27.70,00:11:30.05,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,砂漠を一人で歩いている。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wander the desert alone.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:30.05,00:11:33.80,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ここから抜け出せない限り\N何も見つからないさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't get out of here,\NI'll never find it.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:33.80,00:11:37.73,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺に何かできることは？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:37.73,00:11:44.02,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺の心は　もう病みすぎた。\Nもしものときは頼んだぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is too sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes...\NI'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:24.00,00:12:26.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それでは　こちらを。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:31.58,00:12:34.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いつものと違うな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not the usual ones.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:34.28,00:12:38.26,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,新薬です。　こちらのほうが\Nよく眠れますよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're new.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Those will help you sleep better.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:38.26,00:12:40.56,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうか　ありがとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:55.06,00:13:00.06,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（大蛇丸）あなたの心\N私が埋めてあげるわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fill your heart.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:09.91,00:13:16.51,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ムダよ。　アンタが飲んだ薬\N私特製の幻術薬。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That medication you took\Nwas my special genjutsu pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... you...!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:18.98,00:13:21.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,生きるのが苦しいのね。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Living is difficult for you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:21.36,00:13:26.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,人柱力としての不安と苦しみから\N解放してあげるわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall liberate you from
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the pain and suffering of being\Na Jinchuriki,
Dialogue: 0,00:13:26.43,00:13:29.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,死の世界から導いてね。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and guide you back from\Nthe land of the dead...
Dialogue: 0,00:13:39.38,00:13:43.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,さぁ　飛び出していらっしゃい。\N八尾！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Eight Tails...\NCome on out!
Dialogue: 0,00:13:53.25,00:13:56.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,なめるな　人間風情が！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me,\Nyou lowly humans!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:04.01,00:14:06.01,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(ええい！))
Dialogue: 0,00:14:28.13,00:14:30.16,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ビー）大蛇丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:30.16,00:14:32.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（八尾）なるほど　そういうことか。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:32.33,00:14:34.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺が　あのときのことを\N覚えてねえのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder I don't remember it...
Dialogue: 0,00:14:34.66,00:14:39.50,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺も　大蛇丸ってヤツの幻術に\Nひっかかったからか。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also trapped in\NOrochimaru's genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:39.50,00:14:42.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,では　俺の本当の仇は大蛇丸。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So my true enemy is Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:42.86,00:14:44.78,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ビー　逃げろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee! Run!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:44.78,00:14:48.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（八尾）だが　このパワーなら問題ねえ。\Nいけるぜ　ビー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His power right now isn't a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We can handle it, Bee!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:48.68,00:14:54.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,穢土転生　姿違えど問題ない！\Nイエイ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Reanimation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Different form\NEasy annihilation
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:54.11,00:14:56.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ビー）尾獣玉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tailed Beast Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:58.85,00:15:00.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:16.23,00:15:18.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（八尾）復活しやがった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He revived!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:18.74,00:15:20.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ムダだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:20.81,00:15:22.68,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（フカイ）逃げろ！　穢土転生の体は→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to stop\Na reanimated body is to seal it!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:22.68,00:15:25.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,封印しなければ止められない！
Dialogue: 0,00:15:25.21,00:15:28.88,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（八尾）ビー！　封印の準備だ。\Nここは　いったんひけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee, let's prepare for the sealing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well then...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:28.88,00:15:31.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ビー）そういうことなら…。
Dialogue: 0,00:15:31.24,00:15:33.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,逃がさないよ　八尾！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away, Eight Tails!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:41.03,00:15:43.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ナルト）なんだこれ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,00:15:43.33,00:15:45.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,タコのおっちゃんのチャクラが２つ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakra from two Octopops?!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:45.53,00:15:48.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まさか　八尾がもう１匹！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me there's another\NEight Tails?!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:48.19,00:15:50.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《エー：戻るな　ナルト！》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't go back, Naruto!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:50.14,00:15:52.19,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,雷影のおっちゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Man Raikage!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:52.19,00:15:55.31,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ヤツは　ビーに任せろ》\N《けど！》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let Bee handle this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,00:15:55.31,00:15:58.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《ビーは負けん。\Nそれにお前が行っても→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bee will not lose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Besides, even if you go,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:15:58.36,00:16:01.79,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,今のフカイは倒せぬ》\N《え？》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you can't bring down{\i0}\N{\i1}what Fukai has become.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:01.79,00:16:05.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,《エー：フカイの心の穴を\N埋められるのは　ビーだけだ》
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only Bee can fill the hole{\i0}\N{\i1}in Fukai's heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:16:05.18,00:16:09.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,心の穴…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The hole in his heart?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:09.18,00:16:11.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わかった　雷影のおっちゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Old Man Raikage.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:11.29,00:16:13.33,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ビーのおっちゃんを信じるぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll believe in Octopops!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:31.81,00:16:34.66,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ　やばいぞこれは。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not good at all!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:34.66,00:16:39.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やばい展開　これって天災\Nでも　俺　逃げ足天才。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in a quandary\NYeah, what a calamity
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But escape is my specialty
Dialogue: 0,00:16:39.14,00:16:41.48,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（八尾）こんなときに\Nまた　つまらねえラップか。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you rap at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:41.48,00:16:45.18,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,穴があったら\N入りたくならねえのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you rather jump into\Na hole if there was one?
Dialogue: 0,00:16:45.18,00:16:49.27,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,穴…　心の穴…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A hole in the heart...
Dialogue: 0,00:16:52.19,00:16:55.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,くっそ　なんて戦い方してんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Look at them fight!
Dialogue: 0,00:16:55.46,00:16:58.84,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,親父は　あんな連中と勇敢に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad courageously\Nfought guys like them...
Dialogue: 0,00:16:58.84,00:17:01.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺だって！
