Dialogue: 0,00:17:01.09,00:17:03.13,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（モトイ）俺が引きつける！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw him in!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:03.13,00:17:05.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その間に逃げろ　ビー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a run for it then!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:05.24,00:17:08.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（ビー）モトイブラザー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Motoi!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:08.11,00:17:10.71,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,雷遁！　網蜘蛛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Lightning Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Spider Web!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:13.09,00:17:15.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,やめろ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:18.14,00:17:21.74,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ぐわぁ～！\N（ビー）モトイブラザー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Motoi!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:28.79,00:17:31.09,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,（フカイ）逃げろと言ったのに！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to get away!
Dialogue: 0,00:17:35.31,00:17:38.11,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は負けない！　アンタ　俺のティーチャー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose\NYou're my teacher
Dialogue: 0,00:17:38.11,00:17:41.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だけど今は　俺がアンタにレクチャー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, I'll give the lecture
Dialogue: 0,00:17:44.26,00:17:46.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,アンタのおかげだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe it to you...
Dialogue: 0,00:17:52.74,00:17:55.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((あっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:17:55.29,00:17:57.29,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,まずい！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:14.86,00:18:18.46,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ビー　エーが　なぜ強いかわかるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee, do you know why Ay is strong?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:20.51,00:18:24.01,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,エーは　未来の雷影候補として\N甘やかされることもなく→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ay was raised carefully,\Nwithout being pampered
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because he was in line\Nto become the Raikage.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:24.01,00:18:26.88,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大切に育てられてきた。
Dialogue: 0,00:18:26.88,00:18:28.83,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,雷影様は　もとより→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All that was bestowed on him from\Nthe villagers, including Lord Raikage,
Dialogue: 0,00:18:28.83,00:18:31.36,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,里の皆から受けた恩を\N素直に受け取り→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,he has graciously accepted,
Dialogue: 0,00:18:31.36,00:18:33.99,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,その期待に応えてきた。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and fulfilled their hopes\Nand expectations.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:33.99,00:18:40.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,もともと涙もろく情にあついヤツは\N大きく力強く育っていったのさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy who was once prone\Nto tears and so sensitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,grew up to be mighty and strong...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:40.86,00:18:44.53,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,雷影様の特別な存在としてな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As someone special to Lord Raikage.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:44.53,00:18:47.62,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(特別な存在…))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A special person?
Dialogue: 0,00:18:50.21,00:18:52.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,だから見つけられた。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I found it.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:57.14,00:18:59.24,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,((なんだ　ブラザー？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it, Bro?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:18:59.24,00:19:01.34,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,うん？　うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm? Mmm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:03.79,00:19:06.86,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前は　これから人柱力になる。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You will now become a Jinchuriki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:06.86,00:19:09.91,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,これから先は\N今までのようにはいかん。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Things won't be the same anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:09.91,00:19:11.94,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大変なことばかりだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It will be extremely tough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:11.94,00:19:15.04,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あ～　そうなのってなもんよ！\N前から！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No kidding?{\i0}\N{\i1}It's always been like that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:15.04,00:19:19.14,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,タコにあだ名でも付けてやるぜ！\Nラップしながら！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just give the octopus{\i0}\N{\i1}A nickname as I rap{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:27.18,00:19:30.98,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,いいか　ビー！\N何かあったら隠さず俺に言え。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen up, Bee...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always tell me everything, got it?{\i0}\N{\i1}You are special to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:30.98,00:19:34.63,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,お前は俺にとって特別な存在だ。
Dialogue: 0,00:19:34.63,00:19:37.42,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,(俺たちは最強のタッグだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are the ultimate tag team.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,00:19:46.18,00:19:50.43,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺には　俺を支えてくれる\N特別な存在がある。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have special people around\Nwho always support me.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:50.43,00:19:56.28,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,そうか…　お前は見つけたんだな。\Nそんなたくさんの仲間を。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
