Dialogue: 0,00:19:56.28,00:19:59.81,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,心の穴を埋められる何かを…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That "something" to fill\Nthe hole in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:59.81,00:20:05.40,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,アンタも俺の支えのひとつ！\Nアンタの心の穴　俺が穴埋め！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're one of those\Nwho are special to me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That hole in your heart,\NI'll fill it completely
Dialogue: 0,00:20:07.48,00:20:10.47,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あのとき俺にも\Nそれが見つけられたらな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had been able\Nto find it back then...
