Dialogue: 0,00:20:24.93,00:20:26.93,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か？　ブラザー。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,00:20:28.93,00:20:33.88,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ…　俺は　親父のように\N勇敢に戦えたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I fight bravely like my dad?
Dialogue: 0,00:20:33.88,00:20:37.08,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,ああ　お前は勇敢だったぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah... You had courage out there.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:37.08,00:20:39.01,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,すぐ医療班に運んでやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to the Medical Corps\Nright away.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:39.01,00:20:41.44,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は大丈夫だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:41.44,00:20:47.21,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,それより　ビー　その手で\Nフカイさんの想いを遂げてくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... Bee, carry out Fukai's wishes.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:47.21,00:20:50.71,JAP TOP,,0,0,0,,わかったぜ　ブラザー。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it, Brother.
